name: Neural Edit: Made of Clay
description: Artist: Mario Klingemann / Quasimondo, Original Creation Date: April 29th 2021, A reverse-sound-reactive music video clip auto edited by a deep learning model. All scenes were automatically selected and arranged by the algorithm trying to fit the visual features to the audio features. The soundtrack has been licensed from a stock audio library.
